        %p Julie Locke has been helping leading-edge technology companies build world-class executive teams for over a decade.  She joined Vantage Partners in 2002 and today acts as Managing Director, focusing on driving executive level searches in Consumer internet, Online Media and Mobile.  Julie has completed searches for a wide variety of functional areas including CEO, marketing, operations, product management and business development. 
        %p Julie has helped to build the executive teams at Zynga, Like.com, Retrevo, Ebates, MetaCafe, Google, Tagged, Topsy, Adchemy, Proximic, Podbridge, MokaFive among many others. A recognized search professional with the proven ability to attract and close top-tier executives for her clients, she also has a particular personal interest with products for social good.  
        %p Julie grew up in Ireland and earned her Bachelors in Political Science from Furman University, MA and PhD (abd) in International Relations with an emphasis in Third World development from the University of South Carolina and MA in Psychology from the California Institute of Integral Studies (CIIS).  
